    <h1>How to Rank in Google AI Mode: A 7-Step Playbook for 2026</h1>
    <p class="description">Learn how to rank in Google AI Mode with this 7-step playbook. Build topical clusters, track citations, and recover your organic traffic in 2026.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">SG</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
